{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "ops_training", "channel": "warehouse_ops", "user": "John_Doe", "message": "Just a reminder that there will be a mandatory safety training for all warehouse staff next Monday. Please ensure everyone is aware.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "toronto_process_restructure", "user": "sophie.tran", "message": "I've uploaded the latest version of the training manual to the KM system. Please check and provide feedback.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "toronto_process_restructure", "user": "Jane_Smith", "message": "Thanks, Sophie. I've scheduled a meeting tomorrow to review this with the HR team.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "ops_training", "channel": "warehouse_ops", "user": "John_Doe", "message": "There's been a recent surge in online orders. We might need to adjust our staffing shifts to accommodate this increase.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "toronto_process_restructure", "user": "sophie.tran", "message": "I've been informed that there will be a system upgrade this weekend. Ensure all your work is saved before the end of the day on Friday.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "toronto_process_restructure", "user": "Jane_Smith", "message": "The HR team is planning a team-building event for next month. Let's discuss potential dates and activities.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "ops_training", "channel": "warehouse_ops", "user": "John_Doe", "message": "The new barcode scanners have arrived. Training will be provided later this week.", "created_at": 1620506000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "knowledge_management", "channel": "toronto_process_restructure", "user": "sophie.tran", "message": "Hello team, after the extensive study we've been conducting over the past few months, we've identified some major operational inefficiencies at the Toronto warehouse that we believe are hindering our productivity. Therefore, we've made the decision to entirely restructure the processes at this location. This decision was finalized in our last KM team meeting in October 2025, and we believe it will significantly improve our operational efficiency. Let's start working on the implementation plan.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
